com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registry.properties

Interface EntityPropertyRegistry

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MutableEntityPropertyRegistry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEntityPropertyRegistry, EntityPropertyRegistrySupport, MergingEntityPropertyRegistry

    public interface EntityPropertyRegistry
    Registry containing a collection of property information. Usually for a particular entity type, although this is not required.
    See Also:
    DefaultEntityPropertyRegistry, EntityPropertyRegistryProvider

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String INDEXER
      Suffix indicator that a property descriptor represents the specific member of a the collection property (having the same name but without the indexer).
      static String LABEL
      Name of the label property.
      static String MAP_KEY
      Suffix indicator that a property descriptor represents the key of a map property (having the same name but without this suffix).
      static String MAP_VALUE
      Suffix indicator that a property descriptor represents the value of a map property (having the same name but without this suffix).
